g c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh sinh ho\u1ea1t.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7174\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/15-3-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Do \u0111\u00f3, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 Byzan lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n d\u00f2ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-7175\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/DPNObOSN-17-2-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u00ec sao \u201c<a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/category\/tin-tuc\/\">Tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n b\u00e8, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 \u00edch!<\/a>\u201d. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m trong ngh\u1ec1 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/Byzannoithathiendai\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Byzan<\/a> khuy\u00ean kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi l\u00ean ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh 3D c\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n T\u1ed0T NH\u1ea4T cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0.<\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n b\u00